title: Geographer Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Malaysian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Coffeehouse and restaurant in a restored old building. Offers healthier food prepared without using MSG and no red meat. Some veg suitable include salads, vegetable soup, veg spring rolls, nasi lemak, curry ramen, curry rice, lontong, tempeh, and pasta. Dairy is used in some dishes - vegans to specify. Relaxed atmosphere with free Wi-Fi access. Live music and events some evenings.
